The updates(Feb. 9th) on novel Coronavirus in Korea
 
○ As of 9 February, 2020, there have been 2,340 suspected cases reported, 25 of which were confirmed, 1,355 turned out to be negative, and 960 currently being tested. The contacts of the confirmed cases are 1,698 in total.
 (since 3 January, 2020)




